-azul/watch?locale=UY","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/97yvRBw1GzX7fXprcF80er19ot.jpg","provider_id":337,"provider_name":"Disney Plus","display_priority":25}]},"VE":{"link":"https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/1429786-algo-azul/watch?locale=VE","flatrate":[{"logo_path":"/97yvRBw1GzX7fXprcF80er19ot.jpg","provider_id":337,"provider_name":"Disney Plus","display_priority":1}]}}},"wikidata_id":null,"tvdb_id":null,"wikipedia_url":null,"overview_source":"tmdb","import_batch_id":null,"import_batch_name":null,"imported_at":"2026-02-25T23:03:50.114085+00:00","region":null,"main_poster":null,"images":{"logos":[],"posters":[{"width":900,"height":1350,"file_path":"/tdqzzSDXeCZzCEzZKPLYQuTwFdG.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":896,"height":1280,"file_path":"/5qwasqQmMtNBCTV7B3h2CnqiaA6.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.7,"vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ym6yZnCzfFraQkzstBsfnvAx8Xq.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/dlSvdOrcCjPf9T4P59Jz9dMbU5D.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/7WCiTNx2RYkDmUQ7BEkySnICGLE.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/wyjWPQYTSsvtM46N8suozsbcz0F.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T08:25:49.854+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":90,"tagline":"¿Y si tu mejor amigo resulta ser el amor de tu vida?","homepage":"https://www.disneyplus.com/es-pa/movies/algo-azul/1xHiQk97bJ2F","overview":"Óscar y Eli, amigos de toda la vida, cometen un error en una noche de copas que los lleva a una situación caótica. Obligados a reemplazar un vestido de novia arruinado, emprenden un viaje lleno de contratiempos y encuentros incómodos con sus exparejas."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Óscar y Eli, amigos de toda la vida, se ven envueltos en una situación complicada tras una noche de borrachera con consecuencias inesperadas. Obligados a reemplazar un vestido de novia arruinado, se embarcan en un viaje caótico lleno de contratiempos y encontronazos incómodos con sus ex."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Ce se întâmplă dacă cel mai bun prieten al tău se dovedește a fi iubirea vieții tale?","homepage":"","overview":"Două prietene de-o viață se trezesc după o noapte de beție și descoperă că au distrus rochia de mireasă pentru nunta de a doua zi. În timp ce se grăbesc să o înlocuiască pe o insulă din apropiere, haosul le urmărește la fiecare pas, iar sentimente neașteptate ies la iveală printre foste relații și încurcături imprevizibile."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Something Blue","runtime":0,"tagline":"What if your best friend turns out to be the love of your life?","homepage":"","overview":"Lifelong friends Óscar and Eli find themselves in a messy situation after a drunken night leads to unexpected consequences. Forced to replace a ruined wedding dress, they embark on a chaotic journey filled with setbacks and awkward run-ins with their exes."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Et si votre meilleur ami s'avérait être l'amour de votre vie ?","homepage":"","overview":"Óscar et Eli, amis de longue date, font une erreur lors d'une nuit de beuverie qui les mène à une situation chaotique. Contraints de remplacer une robe de mariée en ruine, ils se lancent dans un voyage semé de revers et de rencontres difficiles avec leurs ex."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"E se il tuo migliore amico si rivelasse essere l'amore della tua vita?","homepage":"","overview":"Óscar ed Eli, amici da sempre, commettono un errore durante una notte di bevute che li porta a una situazione caotica. Costretti a sostituire un abito da sposa rovinato, intraprendono un viaggio pieno di battute d'arresto e incontri imbarazzanti con i loro ex."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"Что, если твой лучший друг окажется любовью всей твоей жизни?","homepage":"","overview":"Оскар и Эли, друзья на всю жизнь, во время выпивки совершают ошибку, которая приводит их к хаотичной ситуации. Вынужденные заменить испорченное свадебное платье, они отправляются в путешествие, полное неудач и неловких встреч со своими бывшими."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"당신의 가장 친한 친구가 당신의 인생에 대한 사랑으로 밝혀지면 어떻게 될까요?","homepage":"","overview":"평생 친구인 오스카와 엘리는 술을 마시던 날 밤 실수를 범해 혼란스러운 상황에 빠진다. 망가진 웨딩드레스를 강제로 갈아입게 된 그들은 좌절과 전 애인과의 어색한 만남으로 가득 찬 여정을 시작합니다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"あなたの親友があなたの生涯の恋人であることが判明したらどうしますか?","homepage":"","overview":"生涯の友人であるオスカーとイーライは、飲酒の夜に間違いを犯し、混乱した状況に陥ります。ダメになったウェディングドレスを交換することを余儀なくされた彼らは、挫折と元恋人との気まずい出会いに満ちた旅に乗り出す。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Hayat boyu arkadaş olan Óscar ve Eli, içki içtikleri bir gecede yaptıkları bir hata onları kaotik bir duruma sürükler. Yıkılan gelinliğini değiştirmek zorunda kalan ikili, aksiliklerle ve eski sevgilileriyle tuhaf karşılaşmalarla dolu bir yolculuğa çıkarlar."},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1433593,"adult":false,"title":"The Red Thread","video":false,"overview":"Abril, a rebellious and daring stewardess, and Manuel, a shy and traditional businessman, meet on a plane and instantly feel an undeniable attraction.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.4853,"vote_count":51,"poster_path":"/y7cqcjztLFbrN4PUmSJYJjiDOwg.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-13","vote_average":7.725,"backdrop_path":"/2pn7qTvwB47KAjRnj20g6oriARz.jpg","original_title":"El hilo rojo","original_language":"es"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.4976,"vote_count":26827,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.903,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":264660,"adult":false,"title":"Ex Machina","video":false,"overview":"Caleb, a coder at the world's largest internet company, wins a competition to spend a week at a private mountain retreat belonging to Nathan, the reclusive CEO of the company. But when Caleb arrives at the remote location he finds that he will have to participate in a strange and fascinating experiment in which he must interact with the world's first true artificial intelligence, housed in the body of a beautiful robot girl.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.7588,"vote_count":14042,"poster_path":"/dmJW8IAKHKxFNiUnoDR7JfsK7Rp.jpg","release_date":"2015-01-21","vote_average":7.573,"backdrop_path":"/uqOuJ50EtTj7kkDIXP8LCg7G45D.jpg","original_title":"Ex Machina","original_language":"en"},{"id":49046,"adult":false,"title":"All Quiet on the Western Front","video":false,"overview":"Paul Baumer and his friends Albert and Muller, egged on by romantic dreams of heroism, voluntarily enlist in the German army. Full of excitement and patriotic fervour, the boys enthusiastically march into a war they believe in. But once on the Western Front, they discover the soul-destroying horror of World War I.","genre_ids":[10752,36,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.1591,"vote_count":4528,"poster_path":"/2IRjbi9cADuDMKmHdLK7LaqQDKA.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-07","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/zbOlpFM306PHE7EP1OELCH5qSmS.jpg","original_title":"Im Westen nichts Neues","original_language":"de"},{"id":872585,"adult":false,"title":"Oppenheimer","video":false,"overview":"The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":19.7563,"vote_count":11389,"poster_path":"/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-19","vote_average":8.034,"backdrop_path":"/ycnO0cjsAROSGJKuMODgRtWsHQw.jpg","original_title":"Oppenheimer","original_language":"en"},{"id":398818,"adult":false,"title":"Call Me by Your Name","video":false,"overview":"In the summer of 1983, a 17-year-old Elio spends his days in his family's villa in Italy. One day Oliver, a graduate student, arrives to assist Elio's father, a professor of Greco-Roman culture. Soon, Elio and Oliver discover a summer that will alter their lives forever.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.8396,"vote_count":12605,"poster_path":"/mZ4gBdfkhP9tvLH1DO4m4HYtiyi.jpg","release_date":"2017-10-01","vote_average":8.096,"backdrop_path":"/fwf4L3r2ZU9ptOB9nOo5nuVLo1i.jpg","original_title":"Call Me by Your Name","original_language":