.  Alone in the desert, they begin to suspect that their reality might not be as it seems, and soon realize they’re being observed by a mysterious cosmic force.","genre_ids":[27,35],"popularity":0.3051,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/qwMKx5t1dd4A2R55LySG8HpJNnF.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-14","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/hPY11YZci4JLbviU26UjyGqYOog.jpg","original_title":"Delicate Arch","original_language":"en"},{"id":6418,"adult":false,"title":"Hotel Chevalier","video":false,"overview":"In a Paris hotel room, Jack Whitman lies on a bed. His phone rings; it's a woman on her way to see him, a surprise. She arrives and the complications of their relationship emerge in bits and pieces. Will they make love? Is their relationship over? (A prequel to The Darjeeling Limited, 2007.)","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":2.2173,"vote_count":887,"poster_path":"/fiWLuGIUAcJtu2hs7KlcZ0O2Ix3.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-26","vote_average":6.895,"backdrop_path":"/kvlXOT8snP7qplRpkOSAZahH5UB.jpg","original_title":"Hotel Chevalier","original_language":"en"},{"id":6435,"adult":false,"title":"Practical Magic","video":false,"overview":"Sally and Gillian Owens, born into a magical family, have mostly avoided witchcraft themselves. But when Gillian's vicious boyfriend, Jimmy Angelov, dies unexpectedly, the Owens sisters give themselves a crash course in hard magic. With policeman Gary Hallet growing suspicious, the girls struggle to resurrect Angelov -- and unwittingly inject his corpse with an evil spirit that threatens to end their family line.","genre_ids":[10749,35,14],"popularity":4.3332,"vote_count":1676,"poster_path":"/AwmToSgf2IL3aHv0QRVsR5KvChv.jpg","release_date":"1998-10-16","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/mGznDQ8opBuRd004ChVWhDqjAyW.jpg","original_title":"Practical Magic","original_language":"en"},{"id":276731,"adult":false,"title":"Above all... Coolness","video":false,"overview":"Two lazy friends (Mimis Fotopoulos and Ntinos Iliopoulos) find a job as ice-cream vendors to pay their back rent. When they start giving ice-cream to poor children for free, their boss, incensed, chases them off, and they take refuge in a nightclub, where they disguise themselves as female dancers. One misunderstanding follows another, until the impresario seeks them out, offering them a job as a comedy routine.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.1263,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/3IS1auO8GgWsWZM8jp2ybmtqQ0K.jpg","release_date":"1951-06-14","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/kYVMT0XFKTyApGQ5K7BC4cF2mxG.jpg","original_title":"Προ Παντός... Ψυχραιμία","original_language":"el"},{"id":860501,"adult":false,"title":"Sabah Yıldızı","video":false,"overview":"Nevin, who lost her family as a child, grows up with her relative Mehmet Bey. After many years, Mehmet Bey passes away, leaving Nevin completely alone. At this point, Nevin learns that she has inherited something from Mehmet Bey and is shocked. Part of the inheritance goes to Nevzat, a famous composer. However, the only condition for Nevin and Nevzat to receive the inheritance is that they marry each other.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":0.1992,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/jps44fqAc7TSSiiZTkrw1XGjuah.jpg","release_date":"1968-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/yt2154x0jHa7px1ek8dV3b2w4ld.jpg","original_title":"Sabah Yıldızı","original_language":"tr"},{"id":6620,"adult":false,"title":"Sabrina","video":false,"overview":"After her return from school in Paris, a playboy finally takes notice of his family's chauffeur's daughter Sabrina, who's long had a crush on him, but he questions his more serious brother's motives when he warns against getting involved with her.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18],"popularity":5.8464,"vote_count":1334,"poster_path":"/e1Po9NDrH7IJZhv89467gJH5FS0.jpg","release_date":"1954-09-01","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/oXTzokKufEGDcX7q5Cwoxlhmqxx.jpg","original_title":"Sabrina","original_language":"en"},{"id":470153,"adult":false,"title":"Un homme par hasard","video":false,"overview":"In order to make a good impression on her new boss at a work party, Léa Faber, a young single woman devoted to her job, leads everyone to believe that she is married to Yann, the pianist at the party whom she has just met. He decides to play along.","genre_ids":[35,10770],"popularity":0.1581,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/73ntb26zj6twKkngW2FDXP0lSme.jpg","release_date":"2003-01-01","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Un homme par hasard","original_language":"fr"},{"id":6961,"adult":false,"title":"The Wedding Date","video":false,"overview":"With the wedding of her younger sister fast approaching, Kat Ellis faces the undesirable prospect of traveling alone to London for the ceremony. While this is bad enough, Jeffrey, the man who left her as they moved closer to marriage, happens to be the groom's best man. Determined to show everyone -- most of all Jeffrey -- that her romantic life is as full and thrilling as ever, Kat hires a charming male escort as her date.","genre_ids":[10749,35],"popularity":1.9276,"vote_count":1238,"poster_path":"/t0AEzycJ6V8dLVlSudCUAA9mzgn.jpg","release_date":"2005-02-04","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/wi8y24BI9sa8XSnH9vFmmYin6Km.jpg","original_title":"The Wedding Date","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt35537372","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148501,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"CL","release_dates":[{"note":"Disney+","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-02-07T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CO","release_dates":[{"note":"Disney+","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-02-07T00:00:00.000Z","certificatio